burlap.behavior.stochasticgames.agents.madp

Interface MADPPlannerFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MADPPlannerFactory.ConstantMADPPlannerFactory, MADPPlannerFactory.MAVIPlannerFactory

    public interface MADPPlannerFactory
    An interface for generating MADynamicProgramming objects. This is useful for the MADPPlanAgentFactory since it allows planning objects to be deployed with the generation of agents. A factory that returns a constant object reference is supplied as well as one for generating new value iteration instances.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan
